Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:06.45,AIR OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(960,1064)}因眩目而逃开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:16.50,AIR OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)\pos(960,1064)}因懊悔而放手
